## Phase A: AdMob Account & Ad Units (External Setup)

### TA-001 Create Google AdMob Account

- **Input**: Google account, game name (`Iron Wall Sky`), bundle ID (`com.ironwallsky.game`)
- **Action**: Sign up at https://admob.google.com. Register **two apps**:
  - Android app with package name `com.ironwallsky.game`
  - iOS app with bundle ID `com.ironwallsky.game`
- **Output**:
  - Android AdMob App ID (format: `ca-app-pub-1616644616833222~9015068869`)
  - iOS AdMob App ID (format: `ca-app-pub-1616644616833222~8994412201`)
- **Notes**: AdMob may take up to 24h to activate a new account. Proceed with test IDs until confirmed.

### TA-002 Create Ad Units in AdMob Console

- **Input**: AdMob account from TA-001, both apps registered
- **Action**: In the AdMob console, create **4 ad units** (2 per platform):

  | Platform | Format       | Name suggestion              |
  |----------|--------------|------------------------------|
  | Android  | Interstitial | `iws-android-interstitial`   |
  | Android  | Rewarded     | `iws-android-rewarded`       |
  | iOS      | Interstitial | `iws-ios-interstitial`       |
  | iOS      | Rewarded     | `iws-ios-rewarded`           |

- **Output**: 4 Ad Unit IDs (format: `ca-app-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX/YYYYYYYYYY`), one per row above
- **Notes**: Record all 6 IDs (2 App IDs + 4 Ad Unit IDs) in a secure location. These are secrets â€” never commit them to source control.

